frames.caption: A miniature ecosystem is encapsulated within a glass sphere, featuring a small waterfall cascading over moss-covered rocks. Surrounding the waterfall are tiny plants and vibrant fungi, creating a lush, green landscape. The sphere rests on a bed of stones and soil, blending seamlessly with the natural background.
frames.description: The scene depicts a serene and enchanting miniature world contained within a glass sphere. This self-contained ecosystem features a waterfall, moss, and small plants, set against a blurred, natural backdrop, evoking a sense of tranquility and wonder.

frames.caption: A small terrarium encapsulates a miniature landscape featuring a cascading waterfall surrounded by lush greenery and moss. The glass sphere rests on a bed of stones and soil, creating a serene and harmonious natural scene. The background is softly blurred, emphasizing the intricate details within the terrarium.
frames.description: The scene depicts a miniature ecosystem contained within a glass sphere, highlighting a small waterfall and vibrant plant life. This terrarium is set against a blurred natural backdrop, suggesting a tranquil and secluded environment.
